arts.ttl: KNVB Cup: AZ see off Quick Boys to book semi-finals spot
arts.sum: AZ Alkmaar are the final side to book their place in the KNVB Cup semi-finals after a hard fought 3-1 win over Quick Boys. The opponents for AZ had a reputation for giant killing in the cup and they certainly made things hard on the night. arts.ttl: AZ Alkmaar turn down FC Porto’s Koopmeiners approach: “Peer is happy at AZ and we are happy with Peer”
arts.sum: As per VI, AZ Almaar's director of football Max Huiberts was unsuccessfully approached by FC Porto for Peer Koopmeiners (24) on deadline day.
